snippet.title: The Dream Team Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Dream Team is a free fan-made video game about Mr. Fruit and The Dream Team being developed by Evan Bouchard.
Release Date: June 1st, 2022

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1922070/The_Dream_Team/
Itch.io page: https://bouchardtb.itch.io/the-dream-team

Trailer Music: VERSE ONE - Skyline
VERSE ONE's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCeyqXIVzy5RnRG-cW6khkeA/videos
